description: Demolition of existing buildings and redevelopment by the erection of a two to six storey development providing 106 residential units (comprising 1 x 1 bed,  54 x 3 bed , 48 x 4 bed & 3 x 5 bed), 1,649 sq.m. of student accommodation (comprising 54 x studios), 2,629 sq.m. of commercial (Class B1) accommodation, 80 sq.m. cafý (Class A3), 56 car parking spaces, 282 cycle spaces together with private and communal amenity space and landscaping.
